	Added basic implementation for missing methods
	[stringWithUTF8String:], [initWithUTF8String:], [UTF8String],
	[stringWithContentsOfURL:], [initWithContentsOfURL:], 
	[writeToURL:atomically:], [localizedCaseInsensitiveCompare:], 
